  m_text: 'WASD - Move

    Space - Jump

    E - Interact

    Shift - Sprint &
    Leave Push Mode


    Go through a series of continuous puzzles in order to escape
    each room before water fills it up completely. Push cubes onto pressure plates
    and interact with buttons in order to activate the next puzzle in the series.'
